      • findSuperParent

        Device findSuperParent()
        get super parent if the device have no parent, return this; if the device have parent, and the parent also have parent, return parent's parent till the root parent

      • getCoding

        java.lang.String getCoding()
        get main code and sub code if device is main device,return main code + sub code of main device then if device is sub device, return main code + sub code of main device + "_" + main code + sub code of sub device
        返回:
        main code + cub code, like B10001 of main device or B10001_101 of sub device

      • getLongCoding

        java.lang.String getLongCoding()
        get main code and sub code contains parent's coding if device is main device,return main code + sub code of main device then if device have parent, return parent's main code + sub code of + "_" + main code + sub code of this device
        返回:
        main code + cub code, like B10001 of main device or B10001_101 of sub device and like bx0001_b11 or A10001_B10001
